  <name>Connected</name>
  <summary
    >High-speed, offline, cross-platform ecosystem bridging devices</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Connected is a cross-platform application that allows you to seamlessly share files,
      sync clipboards, and control your devices over a local network.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>High-speed file transfer</li>
      <li>Clipboard synchronization</li>
      <li>Remote input and media control</li>
      <li>End-to-end encrypted communication</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
